00:19:57,350 --> 00:19:58,590
This is the gift

411
00:19:58,830 --> 00:19:59,960
I, Song Wenchang,

412
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:00,800
prepared for General Wei.

413
00:20:01,830 --> 00:20:03,000
Guess what's inside.

