449
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:16,200
he can rise again.

450
00:21:17,110 --> 00:21:18,750
Congratulations, General Wei.

451
00:21:20,030 --> 00:21:20,870
Yun, since I

452
00:21:22,030 --> 00:21:23,310
