466
00:21:54,270 --> 00:21:55,110
Who are you?

467
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:58,040
My sister.

468
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:02,720
So you're the famed

469
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:03,960
first beauty of Huajing,

470
00:22:04,350 --> 00:22:05,200
Lady Chu.

