00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:40,270
the title of Marquis of Zhenguo

490
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:43,590
of the Great Sui,

491
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:45,360
grants him the Fish Tally,

492
00:23:45,790 --> 00:23:48,310
