517
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:10,750
If you continue to favor civil over military,

518
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:13,160
once you inherit the throne...

519
00:25:17,350 --> 00:25:18,590
Among the generals,

520
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:20,160
only the Wei clan

521
00:25:20,440 --> 00:25:21,590
