547
00:26:26,310 --> 00:26:27,150
Mr. Song,

548
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:28,590
isn't that right?

549
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:42,480
Yes.

550
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:43,830
Yes, of course.

551
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:45,760
Yun,

552
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:46,800
